<BODY>
	
	<H2>Comando faca-enquanto</H2>

	<p><a href="index.html">Tópicos de Ajuda</a> >> <a href="informacoesUso.html">Informaçãos de Uso</a> >> <a href="comandosBasicos.html"> Comandos Básicos </a> >> Comanto faca-enquanto</p>

	<p class="subtitulo">O que é?</p>

	<P> &nbsp; O comando FACA-ENQUUANTO é semelhante ao comando ENQUANTO, permite que uma sequencia de instruções sejam executadas, porém o teste ocorre no final do laço, ou seja a instrução será executada pelo menos uma vez.</P>

	<p class="subtitulo">Como usar?</p>

	<P> &nbsp; Para utilizar o comando FACA-ENQUANTO você deve iniciar com a palavra reservada FACA, abrir e fechar chaves e entre elas adicionar as instruções a serem executadas, e no fim do laço deve ser aplicado entre parênteses a condição a ser testada. Veja na tabela como utilizar.</P>

	<table class="tabela2">
		<tr class="linha2">
			<td><b> COMANDO FACA-ENQUANTO</b></td>
		</tr>
		<tr class="linha1">
			<td><P>&nbsp; 
			
				&nbsp; <B>faca</B> <BR>
				&nbsp; <B>{</B> <BR>
				&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;instrução&gt; <BR>
				&nbsp; <B>} enquanto</B> (&lt;condição&gt;) <BR>
			</td>
		</tr>
	</table>

	<p><b>Veja os exemplos:</b></p>

	<P><I><U>Exemplo 1:</U></I></P>

	<P class="algoritmo">
	
	&nbsp; <B> programa </B> <BR>
	&nbsp; <B> { </B><BR>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <B> funcao inicio ( )</B> <BR>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <B> { </B> <BR>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; inteiro x <BR><BR>

	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; x = 1 <BR>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <B>faca</B> <BR>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <B>{</B> <BR>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;	x =  x + 1 <BR>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;	escreva (x) <BR>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <B>} enquanto</B> (x&lt;=5) <BR>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;	<B>}</B> <BR>
	&nbsp; <B>}</B> <BR>

	</P>

	<P><I><U>Exemplo 2:</U></I></P>

	<P class="algoritmo">
	
	&nbsp; <B> programa </B> <BR>
	&nbsp; <B> { </B> <BR>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <B> funcao inicio( ) </B><BR>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <B> { </B> <BR>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;	inteiro cont = 0 <BR><BR>

	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;	<B> faca </B> <BR>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  <B> { </B> <BR>

	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;	<B> se </B>(cont % 2 != 0) <BR>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;	<B> { </B><BR>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;	escreva ("É número ímpar  ", cont, "\n") <BR>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;	} <BR>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;		cont++ <BR>
			
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;	<B> }enquanto</B> (cont &lt; 30) <BR>
		
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;	<B> } </B><BR>
	&nbsp; <B> } </B><BR>

	</P>
	
